text: William Harry McRaven was born on November 6, 1955. he is a former United States Navy officer. He was the ninth commander of the United States Special Operations Command from August 8, 2011, to August 28, 2014. From 2015 to 2018, he was the chancellor of The University of Texas System. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Military people from North Carolina
